## 🚀 How to Run (High-Level)

1. Upload dataset to Amazon S3
2. Run AWS Glue crawler to create schema
3. Query data using Athena
4. Run EMR Serverless Spark jobs
5. Generate processed Parquet output
6. Train ML model using Spark MLlib
7. Visualize results in QuickSight

